User Guide

Getting Started
Creating an Account
•	Click the Sign Up button in the top navigation bar
•	Fill in your username, email address, and password
•	Select your account type: Choose Tenant if you plan to list properties for rent, or choose Buyer if you are looking to rent a property
•	Click Register - you will be automatically logged in after registration

Logging In
•	Click Login in the navigation bar
•	Enter your username and password
•	Click Login to access your account

For Tenants (Property Owners)
•	Listing a Property
•	Click Add Listing in the navigation menu
•	Fill in all required property details including title, description, property type from the dropdown menu, location, full address, price per night, and maximum number of occupants
•	List amenities separated by commas such as WiFi, Aircon, Parking, and Kitchen
•	Upload up to three property images by clicking the image fields
•	Click Create Listing to publish your property
•	Managing Your Listings
•	Click My Listings to view all your properties
•	Click Edit to modify any listing details
•	Click Delete to remove a listing permanently
•	Responding to Booking Requests
•	Go to the Bookings page to see all pending requests
•	Click Accept to confirm the booking
•	Click Decline to cancel the booking
•	The buyer will be notified of your decision
•	Communicating with Buyers
•	Use the Messages page to view all conversations
•	Click on any conversation to read messages
•	Type your reply and click Send Message

For Buyers (Renters)
•	Finding Properties
•	Click Explore in the navigation menu to see all available listings
•	Use the sidebar filters to narrow down your search by location, property type, price range, or maximum number of occupants
•	Click Map View to see all properties displayed on an interactive map
•	Click any map marker to view property details
•	Booking a Room
•	Click View Details on any property you like
•	Click the Book This Room button
•	Select your check-in and check-out dates using the date picker
•	Enter the number of guests
•	Click Confirm Booking to send your request to the property owner
•	Tracking Your Bookings
•	Go to the Bookings page to see all your booking requests
•	Pending status means awaiting owner confirmation
•	Confirmed status means your booking is approved
•	Cancelled status means the request was denied or withdrawn
•	Communicating with Property Owners
•	Scroll to the Messages section on any property detail page
•	Type your message in the text box
•	Click Send Message - the owner will receive your message and can reply
•	Access all conversations from the Messages page in the navigation bar

For All Users
•	Managing Your Profile
•	Click your username in the top right corner
•	Select My Profile from the dropdown menu
•	Upload or update your profile picture
•	Add or change your phone number
•	Click Update Profile to save your changes
•	Viewing Messages
•	Click Messages in the navigation bar to see all conversations
•	Unread messages display a red badge with the count of new messages
•	Click any conversation to read and reply
•	Logging Out
•	Click your username in the top right corner
•	Select Logout from the dropdown menu
•	Your session will end securely
